Malice:

Malice smiled as he helped Wolfblade to her feet.  She was too much, how was he lucky enough to ensnare her spark?  Oh well, the ways fate work are not always clear.

&quot;Yes, let us go.  I&#39;m sure you will welcome the exercise,&quot; he jested.

He left her very breifly to go and get his sword and disruptor rifle from the weapons locker where Organics had put them.  Satisfied to have his weapons back, he hurried back to Wolfblade and lead her out the base entrance, where he turned to her again.

&quot;It&#39;s quite a ways out, it&#39;ll take a while to get there.  Let&#39;s keep our optics peeled and on the look out,&quot; Malice said as he transfromed into beast mode and waited on Wolfblade.

